==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Transmitter
<hw>Trans*mit"ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, transmits; specifically, that portion of a telegraphic or
telephonic instrument by means of which a message is sent; -- opposed to
<contr>receiver</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Transmittible</ent>⟦br⟧
